ulties in the relationship with the partner, being a housewife or working in the catering trade or hotel industry, undergoing an invasive technique during pregnancy, and hospital stay due to hyperemesis. The effects of anxiety and depression are more negative for the fetus than those of drug treatment for these disorders.
